  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-[#F2F2F7] w-[1024px] h-[768px] overflow-hidden flex flex-col p-8 font-sans text-slate-900\\\"><style>:root{--ph-blue:#0038A8;--ph-red:#CE1126;--ph-gold:#FCD116;--slate-800:#1e293b;--slate-400:#94a3b8;}.bento-card{background:white;border-radius:24px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);box-shadow:0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);overflow:hidden;transition:all 0.3s ease;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}.stat-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--slate-400);margin-bottom:4px;}.accent-yellow{background-color:var(--ph-gold);}.accent-blue{background-color:var(--ph-blue);}.accent-red{background-color:var(--ph-red);}</style><header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-8\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1 w-8\\\"><div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full accent-blue rounded-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full accent-red rounded-full\\\"></div></div><span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black italic tracking-tighter\\\">PILIPINAS</span></div><nav class=\\\"flex gap-8 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500\\\"><span>Overview</span><span>Destinations</span><span>Heritage</span><span>Travel Guide</span></nav><div class=\\\"px-5 py-2 accent-blue text-white rounded-full text-xs font-bold\\\">VISIT NOW</div></header><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-4 grid-rows-3 gap-5 flex-1\\\"><div class=\\\"col-span-2 row-span-2 bento-card accent-blue relative p-10 text-white border-none shadow-2xl\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl\\\"></div><div class=\\\"relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-6xl font-black leading-[0.9] mb-4\\\">7,641<br/>ISLANDS</h1><p class=\\\"text-blue-100/80 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-sm\\\">Discover the Pearl of the Orient Seas, a vibrant archipelago where adventure meets ancient tradition and tropical paradise.</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 justify-between\\\"><div><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Capital City</div><h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\\\">Manila</h2><p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1\\\">Metropolitan Hub</p></div><div class=\\\"h-px bg-slate-100 my-4\\\"></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\342\202\261</div><div><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Currency</div><p class=\\\"font-bold\\\">PHP / Peso</p></div></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 bg-slate-900 text-white border-none\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label text-slate-500\\\">Weather</div><div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center\\\"><span class=\\\"text-5xl mb-2\\\">\342\230\200\357\270\217</span><h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">27\302\260C</h3><p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-60\\\">Tropical Climate</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 accent-red text-white border-none justify-between\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label text-white/50\\\">Cuisine</div><div><h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-black italic mb-1\\\">ADOBO & SINIGANG</h3><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/70\\\">A unique fusion of Malay, Spanish, and Chinese influences.</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 justify-center\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Population</div><h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black\\\">115M</h3><p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400\\\">The world\'s 13th largest</p></div><div class=\\\"col-span-2 bento-card flex-row p-0 bg-white\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1/3 bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl\\\">\360\237\233\272</div><div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 flex flex-col justify-center\\\"><h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-2\\\">The Jeepney King</h3><p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-snug\\\">Known as the \\\"King of the Road,\\\" these vibrant vehicles are symbols of Filipino ingenuity and art.</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-transparent shadow-none\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Top Destination</div><h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight mb-2\\\">El Nido, Palawan</h3><p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\\\">The Last Frontier</p></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 accent-yellow border-none justify-center items-center\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label text-amber-900/60\\\">Official Language</div><h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black text-amber-950\\\">Filipino</h3><p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-amber-900/70\\\">& English</p></div></div></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <div class=\\\"bg-[#F2F2F7] w-[1024px] h-[768px] overflow-hidden flex flex-col p-8 font-sans text-slate-900\\\"><style>:root{--ph-blue:#0038A8;--ph-red:#CE1126;--ph-gold:#FCD116;--slate-800:#1e293b;--slate-400:#94a3b8;}.bento-card{background:white;border-radius:24px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);box-shadow:0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);overflow:hidden;transition:all 0.3s ease;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}.stat-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--slate-400);margin-bottom:4px;}.accent-yellow{background-color:var(--ph-gold);}.accent-blue{background-color:var(--ph-blue);}.accent-red{background-color:var(--ph-red);}</style><header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-8\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1 w-8\\\"><div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full accent-blue rounded-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"h-1.5 w-full accent-red rounded-full\\\"></div></div><span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black italic tracking-tighter\\\">PILIPINAS</span></div><nav class=\\\"flex gap-8 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500\\\"><span>Overview</span><span>Destinations</span><span>Heritage</span><span>Travel Guide</span></nav><div class=\\\"px-5 py-2 accent-blue text-white rounded-full text-xs font-bold\\\">VISIT NOW</div></header><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-4 grid-rows-3 gap-5 flex-1\\\"><div class=\\\"col-span-2 row-span-2 bento-card accent-blue relative p-10 text-white border-none shadow-2xl\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl\\\"></div><div class=\\\"relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-6xl font-black leading-[0.9] mb-4\\\">7,641<br/>ISLANDS</h1><p class=\\\"text-blue-100/80 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-sm\\\">Discover the Pearl of the Orient Seas, a vibrant archipelago where adventure meets ancient tradition and tropical paradise.</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 justify-between\\\"><div><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Capital City</div><h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\\\">Manila</h2><p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1\\\">Metropolitan Hub</p></div><div class=\\\"h-px bg-slate-100 my-4\\\"></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\342\202\261</div><div><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Currency</div><p class=\\\"font-bold\\\">PHP / Peso</p></div></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 bg-slate-900 text-white border-none\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label text-slate-500\\\">Weather</div><div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center\\\"><span class=\\\"text-5xl mb-2\\\">\342\230\200\357\270\217</span><h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">27\302\260C</h3><p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-60\\\">Tropical Climate</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 accent-red text-white border-none justify-between\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label text-white/50\\\">Cuisine</div><div><h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-black italic mb-1\\\">ADOBO & SINIGANG</h3><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/70\\\">A unique fusion of Malay, Spanish, and Chinese influences.</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 justify-center\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Population</div><h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black\\\">115M</h3><p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400\\\">The world\'s 13th largest</p></div><div class=\\\"col-span-2 bento-card flex-row p-0 bg-white\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1/3 bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl\\\">\360\237\233\272</div><div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 flex flex-col justify-center\\\"><h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-2\\\">The Jeepney King</h3><p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-snug\\\">Known as the \\\"King of the Road,\\\" these vibrant vehicles are symbols of Filipino ingenuity and art.</p></div></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-transparent shadow-none\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label\\\">Top Destination</div><h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight mb-2\\\">El Nido, Palawan</h3><p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\\\">The Last Frontier</p></div><div class=\\\"bento-card p-6 accent-yellow border-none justify-center items-center\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-label text-amber-900/60\\\">Official Language</div><h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black text-amber-950\\\">Filipino</h3><p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-amber-900/70\\\">& English</p></div></div></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
}
