  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Summarizing Development Success**\n\nThe server restart was flawless! I\'m now tasked with crafting a concise and visually appealing summary, keeping in mind the agent\'s instructions to maintain a friendly and helpful tone. I\'ll focus on polishing the presentation to make it as design-centric as possible, to meet expectations.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have implemented custom web application designed around the **Bento Grid** theme, acting as an interactive cultural portal and travel companion to the Philippines. \n\n### \360\237\223\220 Design & Visual Identity\nIn alignment with your theme requirements, the application\'s layout is structured around an elegant, responsive **Bento Grid** utilizing crisp spacing and distinct visual margins:\n*   **Flagship Accent Palette**: The interface is framed in beautiful, high-contrast colors inspired by the Philippine flag: Deep Royal Blue (`#0038A8`), Vibrant Solar Red (`#CE1126`), and Bright Sunshine Gold (`#FCD116`).\n*   **Modern Cards**: Every segment is structured using a `.bento-card` format featuring clean border outlines, soft elevated shadows, and responsive scaling translations upon user cursor interaction.\n*   **Dynamic Layout Variations**: Large focal display cards showcase the majestic **\"7,641 Islands\"** statistic, balanced by dense information blocks outlining metropolitan, currency, and language characteristics.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\214\220 Core Bento Grid Modules\n1.  **Archipelago Division Navigator**: \n    *   Allows visitors to navigate seamlessly between the three major divisions: **Luzon**, **Visayas**, and **Mindanao**.\n    *   Reveals regional climate statistics, native language lists, and curated must-visit destinations (including *Batanes Islands*, *Siargao*, *Boracay*, and the physical wonder of the *Chocolate Hills*).\n    *   Each destination features a collapsible **\"Local Secret\"** card providing insider secrets and curated travel experiences.\n2.  **Archipelago Culinary Showcase**:\n    *   An interactive menu highlighting world-famous culinary exports such as *Pork Adobo*, *Sinigang*, *Lechon Cebu*, and *Chicken Inasal*.\n    *   Displays natural pronunciations, historical background, preparation styles, and detailed flavor notes on click.\n3.  **Local Translations Phrasebook**:\n    *   An multi-dialect matrix comparing and filtering common travel greetings, dining cues, and transit phrases.\n    *   Instantly switches between **Tagalog**, **Cebuano**, and **Ilocano** with custom simulated text-to-speech pronunciation helpers.\n4.  **Heritage Trivia Challenge**:\n    *   A fully functional, 7-question interactive trivia game testing readers on local statistics and island lore.\n    *   Features real-time score tracking, responsive correct/incorrect action states, progress meters, and historical background explanations for each choice.\n5.  **AI Travel Concierge \"Bayani\"**:\n    *   A beautiful, conversational interface featuring pre-drafted travel prompts and instant response rendering.\n    *   Connects directly to a secure, server-side chatbot powered by the **Gemini 3.5 Flash** model to provide authentic suggestions, packing guides, and day-to-day traveler itineraries.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      nanos: 242452913
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
